334
00:30:15.063 --> 00:30:16.397
Is it important?

335
00:30:16.481 --> 00:30:17.690
Very.

336
00:30:20.652 --> 00:30:21.736
Be right back.

337
00:30:21.820 --> 00:30:23.780
